  * reefing of sail (0.0 to 1.0)
  * reefing of sail (0.0 to 1.0) (again - origionally:  aero/sail-draft-depth-norm)
  * aero/sail-beta-deg (0-360) lookup table ( returns 1 or -1 depending on degree angle)
